<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.3">
<l>kaṟuttiṭ ṭetirniṉṟa kañcaṉaik koṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>poṟuttiṭ ṭetirvanta puḷḷiṉvāy kīṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>neṟitta kuḻalkaḷai nīṅkamuṉ ṉōṭi</l>
<l>ciṟukkaṉṟu mēyppāṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">tēvapi rāṉukkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring one staff for the little calf herder</l>
<l>running ahead so that his ringletted curls loosen,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who became angry and killed Kamsa who stood against [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">he who, having persisted, split the mouth of the bird who came against [him].</l>
<l>Bring one staff for the god of gods.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
